MyBroadband is the perfect platform to run recruitment campaigns for your vacant IT positions thanks to its large audience of ICT professionals. This includes a monthly readership of approximately 2.9 million, as well as a newsletter database of nearly 200,000 subscribers. This audience trusts the MyBroadband brand, which provides legitimacy to your recruitment campaign and helps you attract more applicants. There are various methods to choose from to reach your desired target audience of job-seeking IT professionals. These options include sponsored articles, social media promotions, category takeovers, What’s Next interviews, dedicated mailers, display banners, and more. MyBroadband’s marketing team will handle all aspects of your recruitment campaign, such as audience targeting, performance optimisation, and reporting. To learn more about how we can make your recruitment campaign a success, contact MyBroadband’s advertising team.